      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 13.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_05-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "そして、私自身も答えを見つけてきます\n勝てばきっと、アイドルがなんなのか分かると思うから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I'll find my own answer too\nBecause if we win‚ I think I'll understand what it means to be an idol",
        "id": ""
