      "text": "（でも月ストは……セミファイナルで負けたあの日以来）\n（ずっと前に進めていない気がする）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(But Moon's Tempest… since that day we lost in the semifinals)\n(It feels like we haven't been able to move forward at all)",
        "id": ""
