      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_05-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "ここから頑張ろう？　今を乗り切って\nこのメンバーで、サニピに追いつこう",
